    {
      "id": "PopularPost276879",
      "post_content": "There is only one thing I don't like about this card:  \n  \nAt this mana cost, and it being Blue, haste feels wrong.   \n  \nI know exactly why it's there, but it being there makes this card play a little too much like the Red family of cards. Also this is an Instant. It is bonkers and wrong for Insurrection to cost half the mana, and be an Instant, in flipping Blue. Blue can get away with playing a low-creature deck, thus enabling to really turn this into almost exactly that.  \n  \nImagine if it didn't have Haste. It would be much more Blue and more interesting to think how this might be used if that were the case.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost276879\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">There is only one thing I don't like about this card:<br/><br/>At this mana cost, and it being Blue, haste feels wrong. <br/><br/>I know exactly why it's there, but it being there makes this card play a little too much like the Red family of cards. Also this is an Instant. It is bonkers and wrong for Insurrection to cost half the mana, and be an Instant, in flipping Blue. Blue can get away with playing a low-creature deck, thus enabling to really turn this into almost exactly that.<br/><br/>Imagine if it didn't have Haste. It would be much more Blue and more interesting to think how this might be used if that were the case.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '276879'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (10/18/2012 12:42:10 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_st